{"tid":815398,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國「弗洛倫斯」增強為4級颶風 美東岸逾120萬人被勒令疏散","createTime":"2018-09-12T04:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T07:02:36.000Z","uid":1221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"261e639bcc0789d491111bcf7552e30c7873aa1a","tid":815398,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgs.ntdtv.com/pic/2018/9-11/p9026701a897465922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.ntdtv.com%2Fpic%2F2018%2F9-11%2Fp9026701a897465922.jpg&h=a70b68bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n逼近美國東南部的颶風「弗洛倫斯」（Florence），周一迅速增強為4級颶風，預料今日繼續增強，有可能成為5級颶風，周四在南卡羅來納或北卡羅來納州登陸，有可能成為30年來吹襲該區的最強颶風。東岸四州宣佈進入緊急狀態。南卡州州長麥克馬斯特（Henry McMaster）下令沿海100萬居民疏散。維珍尼亞州州長下令沿岸低窪地區24.5萬居民疏散。<br />\n<br />\n「弗洛倫斯」最高持續風速達每小時195公里，當地周一中午，位於北卡羅來納州開普菲爾（Cape Fear）東南偏東1,985公里，以時速20公里向西移動。國家颶風中心指「弗洛倫斯」會是極之危險的強烈颶風，可能導致東岸多州出現嚴重水浸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.chinapress.com.my/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/2018-09-11T003317Z_313534045aaaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinapress.com.my%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F2018-09-11T003317Z_313534045aaaa.jpg&h=15ce048a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南、北卡羅來納、維珍尼亞、馬里蘭四州已進入緊急狀態。維州州長諾瑟姆（Ralph Northam）坦言，最擔心的不是強風，而是水浸。他提醒市民颶風可能導致災難性水浸、強風及廣泛地區停電。<br />\n<br />\n「弗洛倫斯」是1989年颶風「雨果」（Hugo）以來，再次有如此行經路線的四級颶風朝向美國東岸南部而來。<br />\n美國海軍安排維珍尼亞州諾福克基地近30艘艦隻出海，駛到大西洋安全位置避風。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180911/large/1536599614_a5dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180911%2Flarge%2F1536599614_a5dd.jpg&h=f0be294b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71d407d48436ebb4aad75ac72e16fd85f15081e0","tid":815398,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:46:56.000Z","msg":"山竹勁d"},{"pid":"f49d8811644a42e383900e308b91345a45033e10","tid":815398,"uid":30377,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:47:17.000Z","msg":"美國人打風: <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人打風: <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d35a6eafc2a8acc777b460f3a5d5215ca5ab0d","tid":815398,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T06:59:05.000Z","msg":"弗你老母洛倫斯<br />\n<br />\n佛羅倫斯呀成日用蝗譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7f7c46a89656e9d14d361028771e69815f6a93","tid":815398,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T07:00:41.000Z","msg":"God bless USA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c1248c5c6e782e662479f9cb3f021338105bcf","tid":815398,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T07:02:36.000Z","msg":"美帝國東岸仲起緊木屋"}]}